{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"34":"Clothing (Kitab Al-Libas)"},"section_detail":{"34":{"hadithnumber_first":4020,"hadithnumber_last":4158,"arabicnumber_first":4020,"arabicnumber_last":4158}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4069,"arabicnumber":4069,"text":"Rapporté par Abdullah ibn Amr ibn al-‘As رضي الله عنه : Un homme portant deux vêtements rouges est passé devant le Prophète ﷺ et l’a salué, mais il n’a pas répondu à son salut","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Daif"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":34,"hadith":50}}]}